{
  "message": "feat(web): Enable React Compiler for automatic memoization\n\n- Configure babel-plugin-react-compiler in vite.config.ts with target \"19\"\n- Add VITE_DISABLE_COMPILER feature flag for quick rollback\n- Apply compiler config consistently to main plugin and worker plugins\n- Add development-mode logging to show compiler status\n- Upgrade @vitejs/plugin-react to 5.1.2\n- Add babel-plugin-react-compiler 1.0.0 as devDependency\n- Document feature flag in .env.example\n\nCloses flywheel_gateway-pjv\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
